/*
  ESP32 Air Dust + Solar Light Logger Web Server
  Hardware:
  - ESP32 38 pin
  - BME280 I2C
  - TSL2591 I2C
  - OLED SSD1306 0.96 inch I2C
  - PMS7003 UART
  - MicroSD SPI

  Functions:
  - OLED realtime update every 1 second
  - Web page realtime update through ESP32 AP IP
  - Save CSV to MicroSD every 5 minutes
  - Download CSV from web
  - View last CSV rows from web

  Wiring:
  I2C SDA = GPIO21
  I2C SCL = GPIO22

  PMS7003 TXD -> ESP32 GPIO16 RX2
  PMS7003 RXD -> ESP32 GPIO17 TX2
  PMS7003 VCC -> 5V
  PMS7003 GND -> GND

  MicroSD CS   -> GPIO5
  MicroSD SCK  -> GPIO18
  MicroSD MISO -> GPIO19
  MicroSD MOSI -> GPIO23

  OLED/BME280/TSL2591 VCC -> 3V3
*/

